Tame the BeaST  --  The B to X of BibTeX
========================================
	    Nicolas MARKEY
     <markey@lsv.ens-cachan.fr>
           v1.4 2009/10/11


This is an (as complete as possible) documentation
about  bibliographies in LaTeX,  thus mainly about 
BibTeX.

Comments welcome!


